data.text: This is a blog dedicated to the best (and cutest) comedian EVER! I realize a lot of the Buster scenes I post have been done before. I try not to do repeats but the way I look at it is the more people on Tumblr who see Buster, the better! He was a great comedian and needs to be loved as much as possible.
